description:
This is a 62 minute workout called '60 Minute Full Body Dumbbell Strength Workout [With Audio Cues]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for this 60 minute Full Body Strength Workout! This is an all-in-one workout that you can do daily to improve your overall strength and conditioning. All you need is a pair of dumbbells to complete this session but having multiple pairs will be more beneficial to challenge yourself for each exercise. Juice will provide audio cues during this workout to assist you with form and there will be modifications provided for more advanced movements. Be sure to drop a comment and let us know how your workout went with us!
